data.title: Raising Victor Vargas
data.meta_description: In this different-kind-of rom-com directed by Peter Sollett (Freeheld), Victor (Victor Rasuk - Fifty Shades Freed), a Dominican teen, lives with his grandmother (Altagracia Guzman) and his siblings Nino (Silvestre Rasuk) and Vicki (Krystal Rodriguez) in New York’s Lower Eastside. After he falls for Judy (Judy Marte), he devises a plan to meet her, resulting in a heartwarming tale of first love and a grandmother’s battle to maintain her family’s old-world innocence.
